ld map to standard Schema.org datePublished rather than being emitted as a\nnon-standard firstPublishedOnline property.\n```\n\n## Cosmic Connections current model\n\nCurrent route:\n\n```text\n\/publications\/reviews\/cosmic-connections\/\n```\n\nCurrent DOI article node:\n\n```text\nhttps:\/\/doi.org\/10.1177\/13684310241249684\n```\n\nThe DOI article\/review node now uses a date-only first online publication date:\n\n```json\n\"datePublished\": \"2024-05-24\"\n```\n\nThe arbitrary previous timestamp has been removed:\n\n```json\n\"datePublished\": \"2024-05-24T12:00:00+01:00\"\n```\n\nDo not reintroduce that noon timestamp unless the time is real and meaningful.\n\n## Cosmic Connections issue metadata\n\nThe Cosmic Connections DOI article points to the issue node:\n\n```json\n\"isPartOf\": {\n  \"@id\": \"https:\/\/stevanveljkovic.com\/publications\/reviews\/cosmic-connections\/#issue\"\n}\n```\n\nThe issue node records the later issue assignment:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"@type\": \"PublicationIssue\",\n  \"issueNumber\": \"2\",\n  \"url\": \"https:\/\/journals.sagepub.com\/toc\/esta\/28\/2\",\n  \"datePublished\": \"2025-05\",\n  \"image\": \"https:\/\/journals.sagepub.com\/cms\/asset\/e55d45ab-8419-4908-b935-0563c55874fa\/esta_28_2.cover.png\"\n}\n```\n\nThis means:\n\n```text\nArticle first published online: 24 May 2024\nIssue assignment: European Journal of Social Theory, volume 28, issue 2,\nMay 2025\n```\n\n## Cosmic Connections local review node\n\nThe local hosted manuscript\/review node remains distinct:\n\n```text\nhttps:\/\/stevanveljkovic.com\/publications\/reviews\/cosmic-connections\/#review\n```\n\nIt continues to be modelled as:\n\n```json\n\"@type\": [\"ScholarlyArticle\", \"Review\"],\n\"version\": \"Author’s Original Manuscript\"\n```\n\nand continues to point to the published DOI version via:\n\n```json\n\"isBasedOn\": {\n  \"@id\": \"https:\/\/doi.org\/10.1177\/13684310241249684\"\n},\n\"citation\": {\n  \"@id\": \"https:\/\/doi.org\/10.1177\/13684310241249684\"\n}\n```\n\nThe local `#review` node now also uses the cleaned date-only value:\n\n```json\n\"datePublished\": \"2024-05-24\"\n```\n\n## Issue name decision\n\nThe redundant issue-node value:\n\n```json\n\"name\": \"2\"\n```\n\nhas been removed.\n\nDecision:\n\n```text\nDo not emit PublicationIssue.name merely as the issue number.\nUse issueNumber for the issue number.\n\nIf a future issue name is useful, either omit name by default or generate a\ndescriptive name such as:\n\"European Journal of Social Theory, Volume 28, Issue 2, May 2025\".\n```\n\nThe internal\/frontmatter field `issueDateLabel` or similar may be used for\ndisplay, but should not be emitted directly as a non-standard Schema.org\n`dateLabel` property.\n\n## Issue cover image decision\n\nThe SAGE image for Cosmic Connections appears to be an issue cover rather than\nan article-specific image.\n\nIt has therefore been placed on the `PublicationIssue` node rather than the DOI\narticle node.\n\nThis matches the cleaner modelling already used for the Christian Right issue\ncover.\n\n## Publications page\n\nThe `\/publications\/` page also reflects the corrected Cosmic Connections\narticle date:\n\n```json\n\"datePublished\": \"2024-05-24\"\n```\n\nand the Cosmic Connections issue node on `\/publications\/` has:\n\n```json\n\"datePublished\": \"2025-05\",\n\"image\": \"https:\/\/journals.sagepub.com\/cms\/asset\/e55d45ab-8419-4908-b935-0563c55874fa\/esta_28_2.cover.png\"\n```\n\nThe `\/publications\/` page uses page-local periodical\/volume\/issue node IDs, e.g.:\n\n```text\nhttps:\/\/stevanveljkovic.com\/publications\/#review-cosmic-connections-periodical\nhttps:\/\/stevanveljkovic.com\/publications\/#review-cosmic-connections-volume\nhttps:\/\/stevanveljkovic.com\/publications\/#review-cosmic-connections-issue\n```\n\nThis remains acceptable for Stage 3.\n\n## Deferred adjacent cleanup\n\nThe first-online \/ issue-date work for Cosmic Connections is complete.\n\nRemaining adjacent cleanup